metadata.name: WAW x Vittoria
metadata.description:
This collaborative art piece, created by Women and Weapons and Amber Vittoria, is a heartfelt expression of gratitude toward those who supported and believed in us. 

Originally presented as a gift to buyers of the limited-time apparel drop who provided addresses. 

Thank you. We hope you enjoy it.
